Package: mlDEA
Type: Package
Title: Malmquist-Luenberger DEA Sequential Technology
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Nahum Caleb", "Juarez Espinosa",
           email = "nahumcaleb03@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides helpers to build sequential DEA technology sets and
    solve the associated input-oriented (CCR) linear programming problems using
    lpSolve. These routines act as the building block for Malmquist-Luenberger
    productivity analysis.
Depends: R (>= 3.6)
Imports:
    lpSolve
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/TuUsuario/mlDEA
BugReports: https://github.com/TuUsuario/mlDEA/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Config/testthat/edition: 3
